    <li>You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on our website.</p>

<p>Thank you for trusting PlantCareApp with your information.</p>